Common UI provider a user interface to show the HotKnot transmission page

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
This application provider a user interface to show the HotKnot the tramission page.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
1. The featureoption MTK_HOTKNOT_SUPPORT should be true.



[Build Method]
make HotKnotCommonUI
or 
mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/packages/apps/HotKnotCommonUI

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

1.It is launched after receiving com.mediatek.hotknot.action.SHARE intent which is sent from apps.

All the source code of this module were written by MediaTek co..
